      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">52.219-6</ph> Notice of Total Small
Business Set-Aside.</title>
      <conbody class="- topic/body  concept/conbody ">
         <p id="d3272e13" rev="FAC 2020-05 March 30, 2020" class="- topic/p "><?FM MARKER [CaseNumber] FAR Case 2014-002?>As
prescribed in <ph class="- topic/ph ">
               <xref href="FAR-i1100931.dita#i1100931"
                     outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                     class="- topic/xref ">19.507</xref>(c)</ph>, insert
the following clause:<?FM MARKER [Why] Amend section 52.219-6 by— a. Revising the introductory text and the date of the clause;?></p>
         <p rev="FAC 2020-05 March 30, 2020"
            outputclass="Ctr_SmCaps"
            class="- topic/p ">Notice
of Total Small Business Set-Aside (Mar 2020)</p>
         <ol id="d3242e25" class="- topic/ol ">
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d3281e19" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
                  <i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">Definition</i>.
“Small business concern,” as used in this clause, means a concern,
including its affiliates, that is independently owned and operated,
not dominant in the field of operation in which it is bidding on
Government contracts, and qualified as a small business under the
size standards in this solicitation.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d3281e26" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
                  <i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">Applicability</i>.
This clause applies only to-</p>
               <ol id="d3242e50" class="- topic/ol ">
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p id="d3281e34" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph> Contracts
that have been totally set aside <ph rev="FAC 2020-05 March 30, 2020" class="- topic/ph "><?FM MARKER [CaseNumber] FAR Case 2014-002?>for<?FM MARKER [Why] b. Removing from paragraph (b)(1) “or reserved”;?></ph> small
business concerns; and</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p id="d3281e44" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph> Orders
set aside for small business concerns under multiple-award contracts
as described in <xref href="FAR-i1117805.dita#i1117805"
                              base="i1117805"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">8.405-5</xref> and <xref href="FAR-i1104008.dita#i1104008"
                              base="i1104008"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">16.505</xref>(b)(2)(i)(F).</p>
                  </li>
               </ol>
            </li>
            <li props="Runin" class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d3281e55" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(c)</ph> General.</p>
               <ol id="d3242e80" class="- topic/ol ">
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p id="d3281e61" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph> Offers
are solicited only from small business concerns. Offers received
from concerns that are not small business concerns shall be considered
nonresponsive and will be rejected.</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p id="d3281e66" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph> Any award
resulting from this solicitation will be made to a small business
concern.</p>
                  </li>
               </ol>
            </li>
         </ol>
         <p id="d3281e70" class="- topic/p ">
            <ph rev="FAC 2020-05 March 30, 2020" class="- topic/ph "><?FM MARKER [CaseNumber] FAR Case 2014-002?> <?FM MARKER [Why] c. Removing paragraph (d) and Alternate I; d. Redesignating Alternate II as Alternate I; and?></ph>
         </p>
         <p outputclass="Endofclause" class="- topic/p ">(End of clause)</p>
         <section outputclass="Alternate" class="- topic/section "><?FM MARKER [Alt] Start?><?FM MARKER [Alt] End?><?FM MARKER [Alt] Start?>
            <p rev="FAC 2020-05 March 30, 2020" class="- topic/p "><?FM MARKER [CaseNumber] FAR Case 2014-002?>
               <i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">Alternate I (Mar 2020)</i>.
As prescribed in <ph class="- topic/ph ">
                  <xref href="FAR-i1100931.dita#i1100931"
                        base="i1100931"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">19.507</xref>(c)</ph>,
substitute the following paragraph (c) for paragraph (c) of the
basic clause:<?FM MARKER [Why] e. Revising the date and the introductory text of the newly designated Alternate I.?></p>
            <p outputclass="List1" class="- topic/p ">(c) <i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">General.</i>(1)
Offers are solicited only from small business concerns and Federal
Prison Industries, Inc. (FPI). Offers received from concerns that
are not small business concerns or FPI shall be considered nonresponsive
and will be rejected.</p>
            <p outputclass="List2" class="- topic/p ">(2) Any award
resulting from this solicitation will be made to either a small
business concern or FPI.</p>
            <?FM MARKER [Alt] End?>
         </section>
      </conbody>
